OL,4,Ccontributed to death of baby at
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FHowever, the plan was not communicated
OL,8,Fproperly when she was induced a week
OL,9,Flater.
OL,11,FOther errors included delays in
OL,12,Fsending Ruth to the delivery suite as
OL,13,Fwell as emergencies not being declared
OL,14,Fwhen baby Gile's heart rate could not
OL,15,Fbe detected.
OL,17,FIt was nearly 15 minutes before a
OL,18,Fsenior obstetrician was called.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/10
