OL,3,C'Missed opportunities' could have
OL,4,Ccontributed to death of baby at
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FIn evidence, Dr Taylor said had there
OL,8,Fbeen continual monitoring of Giles'
OL,9,Fheart rate, they could have plotted a
OL,10,Fdecline and potentially acted earlier.
OL,12,FHe also said a midwife should have
OL,13,Fspotted a significant reduction in his
OL,14,Fheart rate and described being
OL,15,F"incredulous" when he arrived in the
OL,16,Fdelivery suite as Giles was born.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/10
