OL,7,FThe coroner surmised the care plan was
OL,8,Fnot handed over and there were periods
OL,9,Fof "approximately 90 minutes" where
OL,10,Fmonitoring was not as regular as it
OL,11,Fshould have been while baby Giles'
OL,12,Fheart rate continued to decline.
OL,14,FThere was also a chance to deliver
OL,15,FGiles 14 minutes sooner than when he
OL,16,Fwas born.
