OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FThe coroner said even with all these
OL,8,Fmissed opportunities it was "unlikely
OL,9,Fto have changed the outcome" but "we
OL,10,Fdo not known what would have been" if
OL,11,Fbaby heart rate monitoring had
OL,12,Ffollowed the care plan and local and
OL,13,Fnational guidelines.
OL,15,FThe narrative conclusion found Giles
OL,16,FCooper-Hall died from severe hypoxic
OL,17,Fischaemic encephalopathy caused by
OL,18,Fplacental abruption which occurred in
OL,19,Fabsence of continuous CTG (baby heart
OL,20,Frate) monitoring.
