OL,7,FIt follows similar findings from a
OL,8,Freport by the Healthcare Safety
OL,9,FInvestigation Branch (HSIB) which .
OL,11,FIn a statement share outside Plymouth
OL,12,FCoroner's Court, Giles' parents said:
OL,13,F"A catalogue of systemic problems and
OL,14,Fissues that when combined have led to
OL,15,Fthe tragic death of our baby boy.
OL,17,F"This is not the first time something
OL,18,Flike this has happened and sadly
OL,19,Funless more steps are taken it will
OL,20,Fnot be the last."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/10
