OL,7,F"Nationally the NHS is in dire straits.
OL,9,F"Our tragic experience is a sign of a
OL,10,Ftired worn out system in need of
OL,11,Fserious investment, overhaul and
OL,12,Fsupport for the future."
OL,14,F"We are here today not only
OL,15,Frepresenting Baby Giles but every
OL,16,Ffamily that has suffered the death of
OL,17,Ftheir child in similar circumstances.
OL,19,F"This devastating tragedy has ignited
OL,20,Fa small light glowing which is getting
OL,21,Fbrighter..
