OL,7,F"We want the death of baby Giles and
OL,8,Fthe findings of the investigation and
OL,9,Finquest to be the start of hope where
OL,10,Fsimilar failings will not happen
OL,11,Fagain, and any other families will not
OL,12,Fhave to suffer the same tragic loss we
OL,13,Fhave."
OL,15,FSue Wilkins, the director of maternity
OL,16,Fservices, complimented the "dignity
OL,17,Fand poise" of Mrs and Mrs Cooper-Hall
OL,18,Fsaying it has been "an incredibly sad
OL,19,Fcouple of days for us all."
